      this round. The previously-added setChess960Mode() /
      isChess960Mode() / _pendingChess960 fields (from prior v1.0.4
      round) remain in place; the engine restart path still re-applies
      UCI_Chess960 from _pendingChess960 after every (auto-)restart.
